column1: The data in this file are World Bank staff estimates based on UN Population Division, OECD, the Australian Bureau Statistics, the German Federal Statistical Office, the UK Office of National Statistics, and the US Census Bureau. See World Bank Migration and Remittances Factbook 2016 for definitions, data sources, and 2013 estimates. The data on migrants in various destination countries are based on the aforementioned sources, which are by nature updated infrequently and may not appropriately capture sudden changes in migrant stock.   Please include attribution for the data you use as follows: World Bank staff estimates, Bilateral Migration Matrix 2010.
